.Dd April 23, 2026
.Dt MAT_WARNING 3
.Os
.Sh NAME
.Nm Mat_Warning
.Nd Logs a warning message and returns.
.Sh SYNOPSIS
.Fd #include <matio.h>
.Ft void
.Fo Mat_Warning
.Fa "const char *format"
.Fa "..."
.Fc
.Sh DESCRIPTION
The
.Fn Mat_Warning
function formats and emits a warning message through the active matio logging
callback, then returns to the caller.
.Sh SEE ALSO
.Xr Mat_Critical 3 ,
.Xr Mat_Message 3